application.model

Class AirportFlights

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.AirportFlights
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataWrapper<AirportFlights>

    public class AirportFlights
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataWrapper<AirportFlights>
    Collection of flights for a single airport. Flights are organized as two separate collections, one for the arrivals and another for the departures. Each of these collections is specified as object of type FlightsHistory
